<view class="container">
  <image src="http://localhost:5001/images/recipe/03.jpg" class="recipe-image" mode="aspectFill" />
  <view class="recipe-info">
    <text class="recipe-title">炒肉臊子</text>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">所需食材</text>
      </view>
      <view class="ing-list">
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">花椒面</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">八角面</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">辣椒面</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">盐</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">鸡精</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">生抽</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">老抽</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">葱、姜、蒜沫</text></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">烹饪步骤</text>
      </view>
      <view class="step-list">
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>1</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">取出羊肉块切丁，锅内放入油，加羊肉丁下锅炒干水分，下入所有调配料翻炒均匀即可。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>2</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">炒好的羊肉臊子也可用来做羊肉饺子馅，口感更佳。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
